<div id="v470.28.5"><span class="G1161 s">And</span><span class="G32 s"> the angel</span><span class="G611 s"> answered</span><span class="G2036 s"> and said</span><span class="G1135 s"> unto the women</span><span class="G5399 s">, Fear</span><span class="G3361 s"> not</span><span class="G5210 s"> ye</span><span class="G1063 s">: for</span><span class="G1492 s"> I know</span><span class="G3754 s"> that</span><span class="G2212 s"> ye seek</span><span class="G2424 s"> Jesus</span><span class="G3588 s">, which</span><span class="G4717 s"> was crucified</span>.</div>
<div id="v470.28.6"><span class="G2076 s">He is</span><span class="G3756 s"> not</span><span class="G5602 s"> here</span><span class="G1063 s">: for</span><span class="G1453 s"> he is risen</span><span class="G2531 s">, as</span><span class="G2036 s"> he said</span><span class="G1205 s">. Come</span><span class="G1492 s">, see</span><span class="G5117 s"> the place</span><span class="G3699 s"> where</span><span class="G2962 s"> the Lord</span><span class="G2749 s"> lay</span>.</div>
